{"title":"Fizik Ergolace GTX Gains GORE-TEX for Wet Winter Rides in Flats or Clipless","link":"https://bikerumor.com/fizik-ergolace-gtx-gore-tex-wet-winter-biking-shoes/","date":1695821087000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-wet-weather-riding.jpg\" alt=\"fizik ergolace gtx winter shoe wet riding mtb\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-wet-weather-riding.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-wet-weather-riding-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-wet-weather-riding-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-wet-weather-riding-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-wet-weather-riding-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-wet-weather-riding-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-wet-weather-riding-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>Fizik has added a new GORE-TEX lined shoe to its winter line-up; the Fizik Ergolace GTX for MTB, in both flat-pedal and clipless models. Joining the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2023-fizik-artica-gtx-winter-cycling-shoes/\">Fizik Artica GTX</a> range made for the icy cold winter months, the new Ergolace GTX is aimed at the slightly warmer, but considerably wetter weeks and months that book-end them. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Ergolace GTX is largely equivalent to the Ergolace, only with the addition of a proven semi-permeable membrane that works to keep feet dry on the wettest of rides. Here’s a quick overview.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-gore-tex-wet-winter-biking.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-gore-tex-wet-winter-biking-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"fizik ergolace gtx goretex mtb winter shoe clipless\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-gore-tex-wet-winter-biking-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-gore-tex-wet-winter-biking-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-gore-tex-wet-winter-biking-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-gore-tex-wet-winter-biking-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-gore-tex-wet-winter-biking-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-gore-tex-wet-winter-biking-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-gore-tex-wet-winter-biking.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>The Fizik Ergolace GTX gets a PU-laminated toecap and side reinforcements for extra protection and durability. Credit: Mirror Media – Mountain Bike Connection, Summer</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Fizik Ergolace GTX</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The new Fizik Ergolace GTX retains the Italian brand’s trademark aesthetic, with laces tracking up toward the outboard edge of the shoe, terminating at a position offset of center. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>You’ll see this design right across Fizik’s MTB lineup, including the Gravita range for DH and Enduro riding. We have to say, on the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/fizik-gravita-tensor-and-versor-mtb-shoes-go-dh-with-flat-and-clipless-options/\">Gravita Versor</a> flat pedal shoe we tested previously, the “ergolace” concept did contribute to a shoe that offered outstanding comfort.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-clipped-in-shimano-spd-pedal.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-clipped-in-shimano-spd-pedal-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"fizik ergolace gtx clipless shoe clipped-in\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-clipped-in-shimano-spd-pedal-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-clipped-in-shimano-spd-pedal-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-clipped-in-shimano-spd-pedal-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-clipped-in-shimano-spd-pedal-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-clipped-in-shimano-spd-pedal-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-clipped-in-shimano-spd-pedal-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-clipped-in-shimano-spd-pedal.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>Credit: Fizik</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-clipless-tread.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-clipless-tread-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"fizik ergolace gtx clipless shoe cleat box\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-clipless-tread-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-clipless-tread-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-clipless-tread-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-clipless-tread-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-clipless-tread-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-clipless-tread-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-clipless-tread.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>Credit: Mirror Media – Mountain Bike Connection Agency</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Ergolace GTX announced today takes a similar design, and adapts it to more of an all-rounder shoe. Trail riding, bikepacking and gravel fall under its list of intentions. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>As such, the sole is a little more flexible than the sole of the Gravita range, with a stiffness index of 3. That should make it a little more comfortable for walking in when the gradient demands you hike avec bike.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-gore-tex-ripstop-fabric.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-gore-tex-ripstop-fabric-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"fizik ergolace gtx gore-tex semi-impermeable membrane for keeping feet dry wet rides\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-gore-tex-ripstop-fabric-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-gore-tex-ripstop-fabric-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-gore-tex-ripstop-fabric-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-gore-tex-ripstop-fabric-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-gore-tex-ripstop-fabric-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-gore-tex-ripstop-fabric-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-gore-tex-ripstop-fabric.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>Credit: Mirror Media – Mountain Bike Connection Agency</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The highlight is the GORE-TEX membrane, or more specifically the semi-permeable, three-layer PRISM 3L membrane. It is said to be 100% impermeable in the outside-to-inside direction. Going the other way, the membrane is said to allow moisture and condensed sweat to pass through the membrane, wicking it away so that your feet remain dry, and thus warm. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Atop the membrane is a durable, ripstop fabric.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-wet-winter-riding-bca-summer.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-wet-winter-riding-bca-summer-800x534.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-wet-winter-riding-bca-summer-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-wet-winter-riding-bca-summer-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-wet-winter-riding-bca-summer-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-wet-winter-riding-bca-summer-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-wet-winter-riding-bca-summer-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-wet-winter-riding-bca-summer-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-mtb-shoe-wet-winter-riding-bca-summer.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>Credit: Mirror Media – Mountain Bike Connection Agency</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/TERRA-ERGOLACE-GTX-FLAT-tread-pattern-vibram-rubber-outsole-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/TERRA-ERGOLACE-GTX-FLAT-tread-pattern-vibram-rubber-outsole-1-800x534.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/TERRA-ERGOLACE-GTX-FLAT-tread-pattern-vibram-rubber-outsole-1-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/TERRA-ERGOLACE-GTX-FLAT-tread-pattern-vibram-rubber-outsole-1-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/TERRA-ERGOLACE-GTX-FLAT-tread-pattern-vibram-rubber-outsole-1-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/TERRA-ERGOLACE-GTX-FLAT-tread-pattern-vibram-rubber-outsole-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/TERRA-ERGOLACE-GTX-FLAT-tread-pattern-vibram-rubber-outsole-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/TERRA-ERGOLACE-GTX-FLAT-tread-pattern-vibram-rubber-outsole-1-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/TERRA-ERGOLACE-GTX-FLAT-tread-pattern-vibram-rubber-outsole-1.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>Credit: Mirror Media – Mountain Bike Connection Agency</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Fizik continue their partnership with Vibram for the outsole rubber, calling on the same so-called MegaGrip compound implemented on the standard Ergolace shoe, an the Gravita shoes (<a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/fizik-gravita-tensor-and-versor-mtb-shoes-go-dh-with-flat-and-clipless-options/\">review here</a>). </p>\n\n\n\n<p>On the Ergolace GTX Flat, the tread pattern is quite aggressive, with rows of rectangular blocks positioned to interface with the pedal pins. Toward the front and rear of the shoe, the tread pattern goes deeper with the use of chevrons.</p>\n\n\n\n<div><div><div><div><figure><img srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-winter-gore-tex-lace-tidy-800x534.jpg?strip=info&amp;w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-winter-gore-tex-lace-tidy-800x534.jpg?strip=info&amp;w=900&amp;ssl=1 900w, https://i0.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-winter-gore-tex-lace-tidy-800x534.jpg?strip=info&amp;w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-winter-gore-tex-lace-tidy-800x534.jpg?strip=info&amp;w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-winter-gore-tex-lace-tidy-800x534.jpg?strip=info&amp;w=1600&amp;ssl=1 1600w\" alt src=\"https://i0.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-winter-gore-tex-lace-tidy-800x534.jpg?ssl=1\" /></figure></div><div><figure><img srcset=\"https://i1.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-winter-gore-tex-reinforced-toe-cap-protection-800x534.jpg?strip=info&amp;w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i1.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-winter-gore-tex-reinforced-toe-cap-protection-800x534.jpg?strip=info&amp;w=900&amp;ssl=1 900w, https://i1.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-winter-gore-tex-reinforced-toe-cap-protection-800x534.jpg?strip=info&amp;w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i1.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-winter-gore-tex-reinforced-toe-cap-protection-800x534.jpg?strip=info&amp;w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i1.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-winter-gore-tex-reinforced-toe-cap-protection-800x534.jpg?strip=info&amp;w=1600&amp;ssl=1 1600w\" alt src=\"https://i1.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-winter-gore-tex-reinforced-toe-cap-protection-800x534.jpg?ssl=1\" /></figure><figure><img srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-winter-gore-tex-ripstop-fabric-vents-800x534.jpg?strip=info&amp;w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-winter-gore-tex-ripstop-fabric-vents-800x534.jpg?strip=info&amp;w=900&amp;ssl=1 900w, https://i0.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-winter-gore-tex-ripstop-fabric-vents-800x534.jpg?strip=info&amp;w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-winter-gore-tex-ripstop-fabric-vents-800x534.jpg?strip=info&amp;w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-winter-gore-tex-ripstop-fabric-vents-800x534.jpg?strip=info&amp;w=1600&amp;ssl=1 1600w\" alt src=\"https://i0.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-winter-gore-tex-ripstop-fabric-vents-800x534.jpg?ssl=1\" /></figure></div></div><div><div><figure><img srcset=\"https://i1.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-winter-gore-tex-waterproof-shoe-800x534.jpg?strip=info&amp;w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i1.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-winter-gore-tex-waterproof-shoe-800x534.jpg?strip=info&amp;w=900&amp;ssl=1 900w, https://i1.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-winter-gore-tex-waterproof-shoe-800x534.jpg?strip=info&amp;w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i1.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-winter-gore-tex-waterproof-shoe-800x534.jpg?strip=info&amp;w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i1.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-winter-gore-tex-waterproof-shoe-800x534.jpg?strip=info&amp;w=1600&amp;ssl=1 1600w\" alt src=\"https://i1.wp.com/bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fizik-ergolace-gtx-winter-gore-tex-waterproof-shoe-800x534.jpg?ssl=1\" /></figure></div></div></div></div>\n\n\n\n<h4>More Tech Specs</h4>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>GORE-TEX PRISM 3L membrane</li>\n\n\n\n<li>X2 outsole</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Nylon shank, stiffness index 3</li>\n\n\n\n<li>EVA Mid-Sole</li>\n\n\n\n<li>EU Sizes: 36-48 (37 to 47 also in half sizes)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>US Sizes: 4 ¼ – 13 ¾</li>\n\n\n\n<li>UK Sizes: 3 ¼ – 12 ¾</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>Pricing &amp; Availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Fizik Ergolace GTX flat and clipless models are available in two colors; black/anthracite and black/white ice. EU Sizes range from 36 to 48, with 37-47 also available in half sizes.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Both models retail at €189. That’s $209.99 USD, or £199.99.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.fizik.com/eu_en/\">fizik.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/fizik-ergolace-gtx-gore-tex-wet-winter-biking-shoes/\">Fizik Ergolace GTX Gains GORE-TEX for Wet Winter Rides in Flats or Clipless</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Jessie-May Morgan","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"0f4f83c76063c3def8b0879f319c1f3157e7f4d80b4316e9ae2a43dbd93bcb45","category":"Cycling"}